* Iron Raptor watched Shaodw throw the gun towards Prowl, her eyes following 
it none the less, but also turning to see the enemy move and jump over head 
head.
Recieving the projection from Prowl and pivoting on her heel, moving her 
body around so that just as Shadow brought his blade down Iron Raptor brough 
hers up.
Blocking his strike and locking blades with him.
She glared at him passed the blades.*

" Move quicker, strike faster; and you just might have sent my head 
rolling."
